---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'ms';
const post = {
  title: 'Peralatan Graduan Startup 2026',
  slug: 'peralatan-graduan-startup-2026',
  excerpt: 'Pembiayaan peralatan untuk graduan baharu. 0% deposit. Pinjaman penuh 100%. Untuk graduan yang nak mulakan perniagaan sendiri.',
  date: '2026-01-15',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 5,
  category: 'Pembiayaan Permulaan',
  image: '/images/blog/graduate-startup-financing-2026.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['pembiayaan graduan', 'graduate financing malaysia', '0% deposit', 'graduan usahawan'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/ms' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/ms/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/${lang}/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Pembiayaan Permulaan</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('ms-MY', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min baca</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Graduan Baharu? Nak Jadi Bos Sendiri?</h2>

      <p>Tamat belajar. Degree dapat. Tapi kerja susah nak dapat. Atau nak buat bisnes sendiri tapi modal tak cukup.</p>

      <p>Banyak graduan milih jadi usahawan. Kami sokong!</p>

      <h2>Kenapa Graduan Bagus Untuk Perniagaan?</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Ilmu terkini dari universiti</li>
        <li>Semangat tinggi</li>
        <li>Teknologi savvy</li>
        <li>Idea baharu</li>
        <li>Tak takut cuba</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Jenis Perniagaan Untuk Graduan</h2>

      <h3>Kontraktor & Pembinaan</h3>
      <p>Untuk graduan kejuruteraan, senibina, ukur. Beli excavator, lori, atau kren.</p>

      <h3>Pengangkutan & Logistik</h3>
      <p>Untuk graduan pengurusan. Mulakan perniagaan lori atau van.</p>

      <h3>Pembuatan & Industri</h3>
      <p>Untuk graduan kejuruteraan mekanikal. Beli mesin untuk kilang kecil.</p>

      <h3>Perkhidmatan Profesional</h3>
      <p>Untuk graduan apa-apa bidang. Beli van untuk perkhidmatan rumah.</p>

      <h2>Bank vs Kami Untuk Graduan</h2>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background: #2D1810; color: #D4A574;">
            <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Item</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Bank</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Kami</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Pengalaman Perniagaan</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Wajib</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>Tidak wajib</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background: #F9FAFB;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Deposit</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">10-20%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>0%</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Sokongan Graduan</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Tiada program khas</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>Biasa luluskan</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background: #F9FAFB;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Kelulusan</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Selalunya tolak</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>24-48 jam</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Dokumen Yang Diperlukan</h2>

      <h3>Wajib:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>IC graduan</li>
        <li>Sijil graduasi (jika ada)</li>
        <li>SSM perniagaan</li>
        <li>3 bulan penyata bank</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Optional (Tingkatkan Peluang):</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Business plan</li>
        <li>Rujukan pensyarah</li>
        <li>Sijil kemahiran</li>
        <li>Portfolio projek</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Graduan Nak Mulakan Perniagaan?</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Kami sokong graduan. 0% deposit. Kelulusan pantas. WhatsApp kami sekarang.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Telefon)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Dapatkan Pembiayaan Sekarang" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h3 {
    color: #8B6F47;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  strong {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #D4A574;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
